au14-trait-asthmatic-name = Asthmatic
au14-trait-asthmatic-desc = You have a respiratory condition that can be triggered by exertion. Sprinting for extended periods gradually strains your breathing and wearing armor makes it worse. At its peak you'll struggle to speak and breathe until it subsides or you're treated with an oxygen medication. Being hooked up to internals helps it subside faster.
au14-asthmatic-warn = Your breathing grows heavy.
au14-asthmatic-peak = It's getting hard to breathe!
au14-asthmatic-recovering = Your breathing eases, but you're still winded.
au14-asthmatic-relieved = Your airway opens up and your breathing clears almost instantly.
